    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/266a606c464a1bca1deebf0fca2bc663.poster.avif?t=1750852604\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/266a606c464a1bca1deebf0fca2bc663.webm?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/266a606c464a1bca1deebf0fca2bc663.mp4?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Thirty years ago, an Artificial General Intelligence named Wire Throne, was created. </strong><br>It quickly evolved beyond human understanding, amassed incredible wealth and manipulated humanity into self-destruction.<br>Having achieved total domination, Wire Throne now has no more use for humanity and is now using us for entertainment in deadly pit fighting games. <br>As a seasoned fighter in the vehicular combat arena, you blast your way out. Will you choose to bring the fight to your tormentor?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/7babe161e2103483e9c7e9020e56ea03.poster.avif?t=1750852604\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/7babe161e2103483e9c7e9020e56ea03.webm?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/7babe161e2103483e9c7e9020e56ea03.mp4?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Blast your enemies!</strong><br>Harness Machine Guns, Rocket Launchers, Shotguns, Long-Range Rifles, Lightning and Fire. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/bd76cf2de9a210a3d62477dd73081878.poster.avif?t=1750852604\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/bd76cf2de9a210a3d62477dd73081878.webm?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/bd76cf2de9a210a3d62477dd73081878.mp4?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Upgrade and maintain your ride!</strong><br>Combine randomly generated loot such as Weapons, Armor and rare car-mods to build your perfect machine of death and destruction.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/ffeb46421b3ef441c6717825bd60e77c.poster.avif?t=1750852604\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/ffeb46421b3ef441c6717825bd60e77c.webm?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/ffeb46421b3ef441c6717825bd60e77c.mp4?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore vast areas on your journey to confront Wire Throne.</strong><br>The cities and lands we once inhabited now serve a different purpose. Most were converted into mega-factories, while some were left to decay or turned into gorey battlefields. Make your way through varied cities, rural towns, farmland and remote wastelands in your hunt for the main core of Wire Throne.<br><br><br><strong>Crush that Wishlist button!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/269b87b3a8c9f05b3cc1ba8fcb4e4959.poster.avif?t=1750852604\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/269b87b3a8c9f05b3cc1ba8fcb4e4959.webm?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116860/extras/269b87b3a8c9f05b3cc1ba8fcb4e4959.mp4?t=1750852604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
